Package dip.judge.parser

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdjustmentParser
    Parses the Adjustment information block.
    AdjustmentParser.AdjustInfo
    An AdjustInfo object is created for each power, and contains adjustment information
    AdjustmentParser.OwnerInfo
    An OwnerInfo object is created for each power.
    DislodgedParser
    Parses the Dislodged block
    DislodgedParser.DislodgedInfo
    A DislodgedInfo object is created for each dislodged unit.
    JudgeImport
    Imports text or reads a file, that is a Judge history file or listing.
    JudgeOrderParser
    Parses Move, Retreat, and Adjustment phase orders.
    JudgeParser
    First stage of Judge output parsing.
    ParserUtils
    Utilities & Constants used by the parser classes
    PositionParser
    Parses static position list, if present.
    PositionParser.PositionInfo
    Details the position information
    TurnParser
    Parses the Turns of a History file.
    TurnParser.Turn
    A Turn object is created for each Turn detected in the History file.
